    "description": "FFF是一个关于友谊、家庭和乐趣的有趣游戏。你是一个新当选的太空皇帝，你的目标是让每个人成为你的朋友。即使他们不愿意成为朋友。你将在广袤的太空中旅行，把你的善意传播给你所遇到的任何人，成为有史以来最受欢迎的统治者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/2b5e360bc601a91d4bf092fd6f27b9ed.poster.avif?t=1686670053\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/2b5e360bc601a91d4bf092fd6f27b9ed.webm?t=1686670053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/2b5e360bc601a91d4bf092fd6f27b9ed.mp4?t=1686670053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这个游戏中的一切都完全是虚构和编造的，不是基于真实的事件或人物。由于内容贫乏，艺术风格丑陋，任何人都不应该玩这个游戏......也许除了你。你很特别。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/d9777efb709d96904a54a0310875881d.poster.avif?t=1686670053\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/d9777efb709d96904a54a0310875881d.webm?t=1686670053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/d9777efb709d96904a54a0310875881d.mp4?t=1686670053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
